<!-- END APPRAISAL FORM -->
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      I work the eastern corridor and understand what motivates buyers to choose Manly over adjacent suburbs. The suburb draws two consistent and committed buyer profiles. Families who have been searching across southeast Brisbane and have decided that Manly's combination of marina character, village amenity and relative affordability is the best fit for their priorities, and downsizers from larger homes in inner or middle Brisbane who want the next chapter to involve Cambridge Parade, the Boat Harbour and a community oriented toward the water. Both groups arrive at Manly having done their research, and they are genuinely motivated when the right property appears.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      The housing stock in Manly is predominantly established residential: pre-war homes, post-war brick, and Queenslanders on well-maintained residential streets, with some townhouse and medium-density development closer to the main roads. Blocks in the suburb are generally generous relative to the price point, which continues to attract buyers who have been comparing the eastern corridor with inner suburbs and have concluded that the land content and lifestyle premium represent better value than equivalent spending closer to the CBD. Properties on the eastern side of the suburb, within reach of Cambridge Parade and the harbour, form the most consistent prestige tier.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #b98229;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#191817; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Manly Specialist</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Premium Bayside Corridor</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #b98229;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#191817; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Marina Village</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Boat Harbour, Cambridge Parade, families and downsizers</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/wynnum" style="color:#b98229;">Wynnum</a>, <a href="/suburbs/tingalpa" style="color:#b98229;">Tingalpa</a>.</p>
