    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#b98229; margin-bottom:1rem;">FAQ</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#191817; margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Common questions about Manly.</h2>
    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column;">

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What drives property values in Manly?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Manly property values are driven by the Manly Boat Harbour, Cambridge Parade proximity, the suburb's established bayside character and the premium that buyers assign to marina lifestyle access within metropolitan Brisbane. Properties within reach of the harbour and Cambridge Parade precinct form the most consistent premium tier. Owner-occupier tenure is strong throughout Manly, and the suburb's block sizes remain generous relative to what buyers would pay for equivalent land in inner suburbs.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          How long does it take to sell a home in Manly?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Well-priced Manly homes typically sell within 28 to 45 days. The suburb draws families making an active lifestyle choice and downsizers seeking the marina village atmosphere. Properties near the Boat Harbour and Cambridge Parade tend to attract wider buyer interest and sell more quickly when presented well and correctly priced against recent comparable sales.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is the lifestyle like in Manly?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Manly offers a relaxed premium bayside lifestyle approximately 17 kilometres east of the Brisbane CBD. The Manly Boat Harbour brings a marina and sailing culture that sets the suburb apart from its neighbours, and Cambridge Parade provides a well-established cafe and dining precinct. The suburb is oriented toward the water and the bay, and residents choose it for a lifestyle that balances proximity to the city with a genuine coastal identity.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          Is Manly a good suburb to buy in right now?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Manly offers a premium bayside lifestyle at a price point that still represents value relative to comparably positioned suburbs in other Australian cities. The suburb's strong owner-occupier base, established Cambridge Parade precinct, marina identity and consistent buyer demand give it a resilient market character. Growing buyer recognition of the eastern corridor's lifestyle offer is broadening interest in Manly from buyers who previously defaulted to inner suburbs.</p>
      </details>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

